Verify cbash-cli components. Tests live under test/<folder> matching the area.

  test/lib/     — lib
    verify_lib.sh   — colors, box, group, table, theme (visual)
    colors_test.sh  — lib/colors.sh assertions (raw codes, short names, theme, helpers)
    log_test.sh     — lib/log.sh assertions (levels, _log_has_colors, level filtering)

Run from repo root:
  ./test/lib/verify_lib.sh
  ./test/lib/colors_test.sh
  ./test/lib/log_test.sh

Scripts force CBASH_DIR to repo root so they test this repo's code, not an installed copy.
